                  </persName>
             deposed. that he was robb'd on the 1st of November about 2 in the Morning, by 5 Men, 4 of them on Horseback, the other on Foot, near <placeName id="t17210113-43-crimeloc227">Tyburn</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17210113-43-crimeloc227" type="placeName" value="Tyburn"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t17210113-43-crimeloc227" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
