                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17210113-43-off222 t17210113-43-crimeloc227"></join>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17210113-43-off225 t17210113-43-crimeloc227"></join>; that they took Mr. Sheldon's Box out of his Waggon and carried it away, and he following of them they knockt him down; that they went into his Waggon again, but took nothing else out of it; that they took a Mare from him; and that they were masqued and disguised.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17210113-43-person266">
                  Neal 
                  Sheldon 
               <interp inst="t17210113-43-person266" type="surname" value="Sheldon"></interp>
