                  </persName>
             deposed, that about the 29th of October he was coming out of Buckinghamshire, and thinking his Portmantua too heavy for his Man, he sent it up 
               <persName id="t17210113-43-person267">
                  John 
                  Turner 
               <interp inst="t17210113-43-person267" type="surname" value="Turner"></interp>
